<section class="method-section" id="method">
	<div class="method-inner">
		<div class="method-heading">
			<p class="section-label">The Method</p>
			<div class="section-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>
		</div>

		<h2>
			Most meditation systems are trying to fix you. They suggest that you are
			fundamentally broken.
		</h2>

		<div class="method-copy">
			<p>
				We believe there is nothing fundamentally wrong with you. Silence is not a
				destination to reach, but the ground upon which you already stand.
			</p>
			<p>
				Spacious Clarity focuses on real involvement in life. Our practice isn't
				about escaping into a quiet corner or a vacuum of thought. It's about
				developing the capacity to hold the intensity, the joy, and the ordinary
				textures of existence with equal poise.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
